---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import ProfileCard from "../components/ProfileCard.astro";
---

<Layout
  currentPage="intro"
  title="Jeff Goseland | ML Engineer"
  description="Principal ML Engineer with production experience at Walmart and Acorns, exploring music cognition and human-centered AI systems."
>
  <div class="page intro-layout">
    <ProfileCard />
    <div class="intro-content">
      <p class="lead">
        Twenty years at Walmart designing multi-echelon MILP systems across 23 fulfillment
        centers, with documented supply chain impact measured in hundreds of millions of
        dollars. Currently building production ML at Acorns: winback modeling on Databricks
        with MLflow and SHAP.
      </p>
      <p class="lead">
        Exploring where machine learning meets music understanding and human emotion.
        Potential PhD direction: music cognition and optimization as an interdisciplinary
        research path.
      </p>
      <p class="lead">
        Browse the tabs above for production work, research projects, background, and contact
        details.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
